description: Access the On-Line Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences (OEIS at http://oeis.org). Ask for "a nice sequence"; "search by terms"; ask for an integer sequence by sequence number (e.g., "sequence A235383"); or, ask for a well-known integer sequence (e.g., "the prime numbers", "the Fibonacci numbers", "the digits of pi", etc.).
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask o. e. i. s. for a nice sequence
name: OEIS-Skill
shortDescription: OEIS: The On-Line Encyclopedia of Integer Sequences
